Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly into the wavy and twisted sky,\Ninto your hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The distance created between us\Nbecame too big,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because we were always together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your honest reply, “See you…”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,coming from that brash mouth\Nmakes it sadder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.56,0:00:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are in an unfamiliar town, crying
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I want to deliver you a smile,\Neven if I’m not by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly into the wavy and twisted sky,\Ninto your hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel it so close,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our two hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:01:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my chance to show my master\Nthe fruits of my training!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both caught in a Genjutsu…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Yakumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s okay now, Yakumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll protect you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurenai Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurenai's Top-Secret Mission:\NThe Promise with the Third Hokage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two who went in first\Nhaven’t come back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure enough, is Yakumo in\Na state of awakening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two handle\NYakumo and Kurenai…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes, sir! 					– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You handle the nuisance\Nthat’s heading this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:03:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That emblem…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re with the Kurama Clan…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuhi Kurenai…\NHand over Yakumo quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does the Kurama Clan\Nplan to do with Yakumo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a clan issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo is the child I’ve\Ntaken custody of,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the Third Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, by force…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think she’d make it look like\Nshe got caught in a Genjutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then trap us in\Na Genjutsu…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Where’d she go…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Hey! Hold it. 					– H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow-ow… Hm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bean stalk is too damn big!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can’t move…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shino!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genjutsu doesn’t work\Non the insects…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He vanished?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where you hide,\Nyou can’t cover up your scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man-Beast Clone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fang Over Fang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Severe Leaf Hurricane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No chance a half-baked Genjutsu would\Nwork on us fully trained Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Huh?\N– Let go, let go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Naruto! 					– Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Sakura…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s because you charge right\Ninto an enemy’s Jutsu on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Kurenai Sensei and Yakumo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurenai Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who’re these people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All four of them have been caught in\Na Genjutsu and are unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurenai Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei… Kurenai Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s nowhere to be found!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kurenai Sensei has…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one left…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that…\NTo think they’d cast a Genjutsu on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It won’t wear off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s Unkai who served as\Nthe replacement leader
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Kurama Clan\Nafter my father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unkai from the Kurama Clan…\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things won’t go as they did\Nwith the others, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurenai Yuhi, Genjutsu user.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m embarrassed to be praised by you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d like to avoid needless battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over Yakumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may very well be\NKurenai Yuhi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but how do you intent\Nto fight within my Jutsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh. I won’t let you escape…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I’ll pierce your heart…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over Yakumo.\NWhy do you protect her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurenai Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t let you touch Kurenai Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, when will you\Never learn, Naruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto! The enemy’s above you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakugan, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re coming at me\Nwith Genjutsu, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Multi Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clones, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! Mine aren’t just illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yeah! 					– Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-zu-ma-ki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto Barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll definitely get Yakumo…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo has been sedated to calm\Nher nerves and is asleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it would be best for her
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to have a complete examination\Nback at the village hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a big help having\Nyou here, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should also get\Nsome first-aid treatment, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right… Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, please show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’ve been like this the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t look like they’ll wake up\Nfrom the Genjutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for quite a while…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that serves\Nour interests better. Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurenai Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Thank goodness you look okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave her some first-aid treatment,\Nbut she has a deep wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must get back to the village quickly…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m more concerned about\NYakumo’s instability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, their comrades could\Nvery well return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m also concerned about
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how we haven’t seen the three people\Nwho were assigned to guard Yakumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me and all of you\Nhead back to the village
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Kurenai and Yakumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Organize a back-up unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponents are practitioners\Nof Genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be okay alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fully…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…trained body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would cram by the likes\Nof the Kurama Clan’s Genjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you resent Kurenai Sensei\Nfor sealing your Genjutsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person hates me…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn’t want to make me into\Na practitioner of Genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then…why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:15:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure she had some kind\Nof reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would’ve been in trouble\Nhad Kurenai Sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not risked her life to save you before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the Kurama Clan…\NPeople from the same clan as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would people\Nfrom the same clan as you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiba, could you take Kurenai Sensei\Nback to the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m fine…\NI can at least do that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kurenai Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t this incident and you\Nquitting our squad…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somehow related?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kurama Clan into\Nwhich Yakumo was born…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was once a force in\Nthe Village Hidden in the Leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a family of Genjutsu users.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, they had been brought\Nto ruin in recent years,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unable to turn out Chunin and Jonin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a rising star brimming with\Ntalent appeared in the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was Yakumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents and relatives placed\Ntheir hopes in me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the only daughter of\Nthe head family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was in poor health and\Nmy official entrance into the Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was not acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had wanted to live up\Nto the expectations
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of my parents and the clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I got really depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father saw me like that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and negotiated directly with\Nthe Third Hokage for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Hokage whom\NMurakumo consulted
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,realized the high level of\NYakumo’s latent power
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and decided to leave her\Nin my custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the order of the Third Hokage,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurenai Sensei became\Nmy personal teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yakumo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurenai Sensei… She…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe since I’m a Genjutsu user too,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got jealous of the high level\Nof Yakumo’s latent powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genjutsu practitioners with\Nhigher powers than mine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are not necessary in this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. You’d do that for\Na reason like that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A selfish person like me can’t continue\Nto go on missions
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with your lives entrusted to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not just her…\NI’m a hindrance to the Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can’t believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t Kurenai Sensei still hiding\Nsomething from us…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also…get that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s because…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurenai Sensei’s hand shook\Nwith heartache
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when she talked about events\Nin the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the shaking stopped…\Nwhen she talked about her motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That motive is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heart is not affected by\Na made-up story.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then her being jealous of Yakumo…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps she’s protecting someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone so important\NKurenai Sensei would protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be, for example…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overheard Kurenai Sensei\Nand the Third Hokage talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo’s powers probably\Nwill not awaken for a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. But the time will eventually come
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when the dam bursts and\Nher powers will pour out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That power of the Kurama Clan\Nwill eventually threaten
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Village Hidden in the Leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time,\Nwe’ll have to eliminate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Third Hokage was\Ninvolved with the sealing of my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Hokage would\Nnever order something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents died just before
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started training under\NKurenai Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a sudden fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the fire spread quickly\Nand they couldn’t be saved…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my parents were even Jonin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think they would die\Njust in a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a fire in broad daylight\Non top of that…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after that, although I was told\Nthere was no foul play…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the autopsy reports were\Nclassified and sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:21:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way?!\Nlt wasn’t just an ordinary fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents were killed on\Norder of the Third Hokage…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way…!\NNo way could that ever be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Key to the rusted heart’s door
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will always be smiling right near by
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if rains of spears were to fall,\NI will run through it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want to find the joy\Nwithout a shape
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This big dream of mine that\Ncannot be translated to words,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make it come true,\Neven if it were to deepen my wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We stand here today because of\Nwhat we believed through,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I will continue running forward,\Nnever looking away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I’m told that\Nthere is no bright future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll change it right away,\Nlighting it with all my feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is probably testing our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my heart, I gently grasped my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.25,0:22:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are probably searching for\Nthe answer to your tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream is always waiting near by,\Nwith the answers in its hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.46,0:22:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Key to the rusted heart’s door
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will always be smiling right near by
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story I heard from the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story I heard from\NKurenai Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.55,0:22:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is true?\Nlt’s unlikely that they’re all lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.16,0:23:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way the Third Hokage\Nwould think about eliminating the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got to get Sensei and\Nthe others to the hospital quick--!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: “Genjutsu or Reality?”
